{
  "texts": [
    "By overcoming these bottlenecks, the field is poised to achieve a transition from solitary generation to system synergy, and from passive tools to autonomous agents.",
    "Integration and Synergy.Addressing the shortcomings of LLMs in weak bug detection capability and incorrect test oracles, deep synergy with traditional automation techniques offers a direct path to a solution.",
    "This synergistic approach manifests in two key forms, namely integrating with traditional automation techniques to create more robust hybrid systems and collaborating with human developers to create more effective assistive tools.",
    "Both avenues leverage the complementary strengths of LLMs and existing software engineering assets, whether technical or human.Synergy with Traditional Automation.",
    "To directly address the weak bug detection and fragile generalization capabilities of standalone LLMs, challenges rooted in their lack of systematic rigor, a powerful opportunity lies in creating synergistic hybrids with traditional automation techniques."
  ]
}